00:31:42.068 --> 00:31:47.193
smaller like level,
and like the landlords--so it's

00:31:47.193 --> 00:31:52.458
kind of like they are--
like the White Tiger was more

00:31:52.458 --> 00:31:57.520
into like hitting the number one
driver rather than like the

00:31:57.520 --> 00:31:58.980
system itself.
 

00:31:58.980 --> 00:32:03.729
Prof: Right and so the
idea is the displacement of

00:32:03.729 --> 00:32:08.563
hostility to the huge system
